# update an old RRD file to the current format for
#	@libexecdir@/dcc-stats-collect
#   [-x]	    debugging
#   [-D data-dir]   where to find the rrdtool files
#   [-h dcc_homedir]
#   [-T @RRDTOOL@]  see the FreeBSD package or elsewhere
#   file1, ...


